{"tid":2482164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港超限戰】  香港人，戰鬥。","createTime":"2021-04-09T19:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T20:51:06.000Z","uid":154486,"like":79,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2650721754b45f0623b1315456fa4f8ebe22a6b7","tid":2482164,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T19:56:50.000Z","msg":"我地既超限戰<br />\n就係<br />\n超越自己極限既戰鬥<br />\n<br />\n共產黨以為香港人已經到左極限<br />\n甚至連我地自己，都以為自己到左極限<br />\n<br />\n好似操體能咁<br />\n當全身所有關節已經痛撚到覺得好似做多一下就會死果陣<br />\n發自內心既每一下掙扎<br />\n先係操練成效最大既時候<br />\n<br />\n只有係黎明最撚黑暗既時候<br />\n擦出既火花先會係最光亮<br />\n<br />\n唔好等啦咁多位。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>光復香港，</strong></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>時代革命。</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7f2353f1cc49e78f0c29e3b6137a82d415137086","tid":2482164,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T19:59:04.000Z","msg":"你係呢個時代踏出既每一步<br />\n就係香港民族心中不可磨滅既烙印"},{"pid":"9864e87eb9693248b5e2e7c0ca6a94389e8865ef","tid":2482164,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T20:01:15.000Z","msg":"【599G】無論點，唔好停，唔好比人閘住，BE WATER。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2482151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2482151</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人仲會繼續戰鬥落去"},{"pid":"f9f42d410ce0c123e084679a85f2d85061f447cb","tid":2482164,"uid":268410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T20:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf44b892b454ce9c726ffda16b7a23f3fd2640a","tid":2482164,"uid":318928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T20:02:47.000Z","msg":"時間 地點？"},{"pid":"a174ca2345f1745dae49529112dee45d184f62fe","tid":2482164,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdf44b892b454ce9c726ffda16b7a23f3fd2640a","tid":2482164,"uid":318928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-09T20:02:47.0